"to :math:`\\text{kwota podatku} = \\text{cena sprzedaży} \\times "
"\\text{stawka podatkowa}`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:71
msgid ""
"A product has a sales price of $1000, and we apply a "
