#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:617
msgid "Public Administration Businesses (B2G)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:619
msgid ""
":abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` businesses are subjected to more control "
"than private businesses as they handle public money coming from taxpayers. "
"The :abbr:`EDI (Electronic Data Interchange)` process adds some steps to "
"the :ref:`regular one <localizations/italy/e-invoicing-process>`, "
"as :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` businesses can **accept** or "
"**refuse** invoices."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:625
msgid ""
":abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` businesses have a 6-digit "
"long :guilabel:`Destination Code`, also called :abbr:`CUU (Codice Univoco "
"Ufficio)`, that is **mandatory**, **PEC** address cannot be used in this "
"case."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:630
msgid ""
"`Complete list of businesses that belong to the Public Administration along "
"with their Destination Code <https://www.agenziaentrate.gov.it/portale/web/"
"guest/aree-tematiche/fatturazione-elettronica>`_"
msgstr ""
"Pełna lista firm należących do administracji publicznej wraz z ich kodami "
"przeznaczenia <https://www.agenziaentrate.gov.it/portale/web/guest/aree-"
"tematiche/fatturazione-elettronica>"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:636
msgid "CIG, CUP, DatiOrdineAcquisto"
msgstr "CIG, CUP, DatiOrdineAcquisto"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:638
msgid ""
"To ensure the effective traceability of payments by public administrations, "
"electronic invoices issued to public administrations must contain:"
msgstr ""
"Aby zapewnić skuteczną identyfikowalność płatności przez administrację "
"publiczną, faktury elektroniczne wystawione administracji publicznej muszą "
"zawierać:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:641
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`CIG (Codice Identificativo Gara)`, except in cases of exclusion "
"from traceability obligations provided by law n. 136 of August 13, 2010;"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:643
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`CUP (Codice Unico di Progetto)`, in case of invoices related to "
"public works."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`CUP (Codice Unico di Progetto)`, w przypadku faktur związanych z "
"robotami publicznymi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:645
msgid ""
"If the XML file requires it, the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia Delle Entrate)` can "
"*only* proceed payments of electronic invoices when the XML file contains "
"a :abbr:`CIG (Codice Identificativo Gara)` and :abbr:`CUP (Codice Unico di "
"Progetto)`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:650
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`CUP (Codice Unico di Progetto)` and the :abbr:`CIG (Codice "
"Identificativo Gara)` must be included in one of the `DatiOrdineAcquisto`, "
"`DatiContratto`, `DatiConvenzione`, `DateRicezione`, or "
"`DatiFattureCollegate` XML tags."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`CUP (Codice Unico di Progetto)` i :abbr:`CIG (Codice Identificativo "
"Gara)` muszą być zawarte w jednym z tagów XML `DatiOrdineAcquisto`, "
"`DatiContratto`, `DatiConvenzione`, `DateRicezione` lub "
"`DatiFattureCollegate`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:654
msgid ""
"These correspond to the elements named :guilabel:`CodiceCUP` "
"and :guilabel:`CodiceCIG` of the electronic invoice XML file, whose table "
"can be found on the government `website <http://www.fatturapa.gov.it/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Odpowiadają one elementom o nazwach :guilabel:`CodiceCUP` "
"i :guilabel:`CodiceCIG` pliku XML faktury elektronicznej, których tabelę "
"można znaleźć na rządowej stronie internetowej <http://www.fatturapa.gov.it/"
">."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:661
msgid "Split Payment"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:663
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Split Payment` mechanism behaves much "
"like :ref:`localizations/italy/reverse-charge`."
msgstr ""
"Mechanizm :guilabel:`Podzielonej płatności` działa podobnie "
"jak :ref:`localizations/italy/reverse-charge`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:666
msgid ""
"When an Italian company bills a :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` business "
"- for example, cleaning services for a public building - the :abbr:`PA "
"(Public Administration)` business self-reports the VAT to the Tax Agency "
"themselves, and the vendor just has to select the appropriate tax with the "
"right :guilabel:`Tax Exemption` for their invoice lines."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:671
msgid ""
"The specific :guilabel:`Scissione dei Pagamenti` fiscal position is "
"available to deal with partners belonging to the :abbr:`PA (Public "
"Administration)`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:682
msgid "Qualified electronic signature"
msgstr "Kwalifikowany podpis elektroniczny"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:684
msgid ""
"Invoices and bills intended for the :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` must "
"include a **qualified electronic signature** when submitted through "
"the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`. This signature is automatically "
"applied in the :abbr:`XAdES (XML Advanced Electronic Signature)` format when "
"the invoice's partner has a 6-digit long :guilabel:`Destination Code` (which "
"indicates a :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` business)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:691
msgid ""
"When such an invoice is transmitted to the Tax Agency, the generated `.xml` "
"file is signed on the Odoo servers, returned to the database, and attached "
"to the invoice automatically."
msgstr ""
"Kiedy taka faktura jest przekazywana do Urzędu Skarbowego, wygenerowany plik "
"`.xml` jest podpisywany na serwerach Odoo, zwracany do bazy danych i "
"automatycznie dołączany do faktury."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:697
msgid "Acceptance or Refusal"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:699
msgid ""
"After receiving the invoice through the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di "
"Interscambio)`, the :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` business has 15 days "
"to accept the invoice. If it does, then the process ends here. If "
"the :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` business refuses the invoice, it is "
"still considered valid once it is accepted by the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di "
"Interscambio)`. You then have to issue a credit note to compensate and send "
"it to the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:708
msgid "Expired Terms"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:710
msgid ""
"If the :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` business doesn't reply within 15 "
"days, you need to contact the :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` business "
"directly, sending them both the invoice and the received deadline "
"notification by email. You can make an arrangement with them and manually "
"set the correct :guilabel:`SdI State` on your invoice."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:718
msgid "Point of Sale fiscal printers"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:721
msgid ""
"Fiscal printers are distinct from :doc:`ePOS printers </applications/sales/"
"point_of_sale/configuration/epos_printers>`. The IP address for a fiscal "
"printer should not be entered in the ePOS IP address settings."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:725
msgid ""
"Fiscal regulations mandate using certified RT devices, such as RT printers "
"or RT servers, to ensure compliant sales receipts and secure communication "
"with the Tax Authority. These devices automatically transmit fiscal data "
"daily. RT printers, designed for individual POS terminals, handle "
"transactions, print receipts, and report to the authorities, ensuring data "
"integrity and compliance."
msgstr ""
"Przepisy fiskalne wymagają używania certyfikowanych urządzeń RT, takich jak "
"drukarki RT lub serwery RT, aby zapewnić zgodne paragony sprzedaży i "
"bezpieczną komunikację z Urzędem Skarbowym. Te urządzenia automatycznie "
"przesyłają dane fiskalne codziennie. Drukarki RT, zaprojektowane dla "
"pojedynczych terminali PoS, obsługują transakcje, drukują paragony i "
"raportują do władz, zapewniając integralność danych i zgodność."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:733
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:57
msgid "Simulation mode"
msgstr "Tryb symulacji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:736
msgid ""
"Since the simulation mode sends data to the authorities, it should only be "
"enabled at the very start of the printer's configuration process. Once the "
"printer is switched to the production mode, it cannot be reverted to the "
"simulation mode."
msgstr ""
"Ponieważ tryb symulacji wysyła dane do władz, powinien być włączony tylko na "
"samym początku procesu konfiguracji drukarki. Po przełączeniu drukarki w "
"tryb produkcyjny nie można jej cofnąć do trybu symulacji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:740
msgid ""
"To test the fiscal printer setup with Odoo, configure the fiscal printer in "
"the simulation mode as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Aby przetestować konfigurację drukarki fiskalnej z Odoo, skonfiguruj "
"drukarkę fiskalną w trybie symulacji w następujący sposób:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:743
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:774
msgid ""
"Make sure the fiscal printer is set to its default state: printer on, start-"
"up cycle complete, and no transaction in progress."
msgstr ""
"Upewnij się, że drukarka fiskalna jest ustawiona w stanie domyślnym: "
"drukarka włączona, cykl rozruchowy zakończony i brak transakcji w toku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:745
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:776
msgid "Type `3333`."
msgstr "Wpisz `3333`."

