msgstr ""
"Uzyskaj dostęp do drukarki, otwierając przeglądarkę internetową i wpisując "
"`https://<ip-twojej-drukarki>` na pasku adresu. Pojawi się komunikat "
"bezpieczeństwa :guilabel:`Ostrzeżenie: Potencjalne zagrożenie "
"bezpieczeństwa`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:791
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Advanced` to show the certificate approval options."
msgstr ""
"Kliknij :guilabel:`Zaawansowane`, aby wyświetlić opcje zatwierdzenia "
"certyfikatu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:792
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Proceed` to validate the certificate."
msgstr "Kliknij :guilabel:`Kontynuuj`, aby zatwierdzić certyfikat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:794
msgid ""
"Then, to ensure :doc:`Odoo Point of Sale </applications/sales/"
"point_of_sale>` is configured with the fiscal printer, go "
"to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Configuration --> Settings`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Connected Devices` section, add the IP address in "
"the :guilabel:`Italian Fiscal Printer IP address` and enable :guilabel:`Use "
"HTTPS`."
msgstr ""
"Następnie, aby upewnić się, że :doc:`Punkt Sprzedaży </applications/sales/"
"point_of_sale>` Odoo jest skonfigurowany z drukarką fiskalną, przejdź "
"do :menuselection:`Punkt Sprzedaży --> Konfiguracja --> Ustawienia`. W "
"sekcji :guilabel:`Podłączone urządzenia` dodaj adres IP w "
"polu :guilabel:`Adres IP włoskiej drukarki fiskalnej` i "
"włącz :guilabel:`Użyj HTTPS`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:802
msgid "Ri.Ba. (Ricevuta Bancaria)"
msgstr "Ri.Ba. (Ricevuta Bancaria)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:804
msgid ""
":abbr:`Ri.Ba. (Ricevuta Bancaria)` is a payment method widely used in Italy "
"where vendors request payments through their bank, which forwards the "
"request to the customer's own bank and takes responsibility for the "
"collection. This enables payment automation and reduces risks for the vendor."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:808
msgid ""
"The vendor generally uploads a fixed-format text file with the list of "
"payments to the bank's web portal."
msgstr ""
"Sprzedawca zazwyczaj przesyła plik tekstowy o stałym formacie z listą "
"płatności do portalu internetowego banku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:812
msgid ""
":abbr:`Ri.Ba. (Ricevute Bancarie)` are exclusively for **domestic payments** "
"in Italy. For recurring international payments, please use `SEPA Direct Debt "
"(SDD) <../accounting/payments/batch_sdd>`_"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:820
msgid ""
"Check that the `l10n_it_riba` module is :ref:`installed <general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"Sprawdź, czy moduł `l10n_it_riba` jest :ref:`zainstalowany <general/"
"install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:821
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Users & Companies --> Companies` and "
"select the company that will use :abbr:`Ri.Ba. (Ricevute Bancarie)`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:823
msgid "Fill out the required :guilabel:`SIA Code`."
msgstr "Wypełnij wymagane pole :guilabel:`Kod SIA`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid "The company's SIA code"
msgstr "Kod SIA firmy"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:829
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`SIA Code` identifies businesses within the Italian banking "
"network and is used to receive money through specific payment methods. It "
"consists of one letter and four digits (e.g., T1234) and can usually be "
"found on the bank's portal or obtained by contacting the bank."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kod SIA` identyfikuje przedsiębiorstwa w włoskiej sieci bankowej "
"i jest używany do otrzymywania pieniędzy za pomocą określonych metod "
"płatności. Składa się z jednej litery i czterech cyfr (np. T1234) i "
"zazwyczaj można go znaleźć na portalu banku lub uzyskać kontaktując się z "
"bankiem."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:834
msgid "Ensure the Company's bank account has an Italian IBAN."
msgstr "Upewnij się, że konto bankowe firmy ma włoski numer IBAN."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:837
msgid "How to configure :doc:`Bank Accounts <../accounting/bank>`"
msgstr "Jak skonfigurować :doc:`Konta bankowe <../accounting/bank>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:842
msgid "Accept Ri.Ba. for your invoices"
msgstr "Akceptuj Ri.Ba. dla swoich faktur"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:844
msgid ""
"Payments of type :abbr:`Ri.Ba. (Ricevuta Bancaria)` can be registered from "
"the :guilabel:`Invoices` (:menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> "
"Invoices`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:848
msgid ""
"Make sure that your invoice involves a Partner that has a bank account with "
"an Italian IBAN."
msgstr ""
"Upewnij się, że Twoja faktura dotyczy partnera, który ma konto bankowe z "
"włoskim numerem IBAN."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:850
msgid "Then, all Payments must be grouped in a **Batch Payment**."
msgstr ""
"Następnie wszystkie płatności muszą być zgrupowane w **Płatności zbiorcze**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:853
msgid ":doc:`Batch Payments <../accounting/payments>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Płatności zbiorcze <../accounting/payments>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:854
msgid ":doc:`Create a Batch Payment <../accounting/payments/batch>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Utwórz płatność zbiorczą <../accounting/payments/batch>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:856
msgid ""
"Once you press the :guilabel:`Validate` button for the Batch Payment, "
"the :abbr:`Ri.Ba. (Ricevuta Bancaria)` file is generated and attached to the "
"Batch Payment, so you can download it and upload it through your bank's web "
"portal."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:None
msgid "The Ri.Ba. file attached"
msgstr "Załączony plik Ri.Ba."

