#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:159
msgid ""
"With :doc:`developer mode <../../general/developer_mode>` activated, open "
"the **Settings** app and go to :menuselection:`Technical --> Scheduled "
"Actions`."
msgstr ""
"Po aktywowaniu :doc:`trybu programisty <../../general/developer_mode>` "
"otwórz aplikację **Ustawienia** i przejdź do :menuselection:`Techniczne --> "
"Zaplanowane działania`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:161
msgid ""
"Search for and open :guilabel:`Polish eInvoice: Download vendor bills from "
"KSeF`."
msgstr ""
"Wyszukaj i otwórz :guilabel:`Polska eFaktura: Pobierz rachunki dostawców z "
"KSeF`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:162
