"pozycjami fiskalnymi, raportowaniem oraz predefiniowany plan kont "
"dostosowany do standardów Tajwanu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:44
msgid ""
"The Taiwanese localization package provides the following key features to "
"ensure compliance with local fiscal and accounting regulations:"
