msgid "For example `https://yourcompany.odoo.com/payment/aps/return`."
msgstr "Na przykład `https://yourcompany.odoo.com/payment/aps/return`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/amazon_payment_services.rst:0
msgid ""
"Enter your database URL followed by `/payment/aps/webhook` in "
"the :guilabel:`Direct Transaction Feedback` and :guilabel:`Notification URL` "
"fields."
msgstr ""
"Wprowadź adres URL swojej bazy danych, a następnie `/payment/aps/webhook` w "
"polach :guilabel:`Direct Transaction Feedback` i :guilabel:`Notification "
"URL`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/amazon_payment_services.rst:0
msgid "For example `https://yourcompany.odoo.com/payment/aps/webhook`."
msgstr "Na przykład `https://yourcompany.odoo.com/payment/aps/webhook`."

