"handling failed transactions: Enable :guilabel:`User Trap` to redirect users "
"back to the payment page and allow them to attempt another deposit "
"or :guilabel:`Decline Recovery` to display a popup suggesting alternative or "
"similar payment methods."
msgstr ""
